Nippon Oil and Fats Co Ltd is issuing a70 mln dlr equity warrant eurobond due July 15, 1992 with anindicated coupon of 1-3/8 pct and par pricing, lead managerYamaichi International (Europe) Ltd said.    The issue is guaranteed by Fuji Bank Ltd and final termswill be fixed on June 25. The selling concession is 1-1/2 pctwhile management and underwriting combined pays 3/4 pct.    The issue is available in denominations of 5,000 dlrs andwill be listed in Luxembourg. The payment date is July 15 andthe warrants are exercisable from July 29, 1987 until June 30,1992. REUTER&#3;